Title: Articles should open from any new content preview
Steps: Articles should open from any new content preview using the same Manual suite as any article in the mixed feed

Title: Videos should open from any new content preview
Steps: Videos should open from any new content preview using the same Manual suite as the mixed feed

Title: VSM content should open from any new content preview
Steps: VSM content should open from any new content preview using the same Manual suite as the mixed feed.  This should include the special case scenarios such as opening game stories in native chrome.
